==Policy== The Eight Musts are:<ref>[http://chinadigitaltimes.net/2013/01/the-xi-administration-introduces-the-eight-musts/ The Xi Administration Introduces “Eight Musts”] 2015-03-22</ref> *we must persist in the dominant role of the people; 必须坚持人民主体地位; ''Bìxū jiānchí rénmín zhǔtǐ dìwèi'' *we must persist in liberating and developing [[Socialist market economy|social productive forces]]; 必须坚持解放和发展社会生产力; ''Bìxū jiānchí jiěfàng hé fāzhǎn shèhuì shēngchǎnlì'' *we must persist in moving [[reform and opening-up]] forward; 必须坚持推进改革开放; ''Bìxū jiānchí tuījìn gǎigékāifàng'' *we must persist in safeguarding social fairness and justice; 必须坚持维护社会公平正义; ''Bìxū jiānchí wéihù shèhuì gōngpíng zhèngyì'' *we must persist in marching the path of being well-to-do together; 必须坚持走共同富裕道路; ''Bìxū jiānchí zǒu gòngtóng fùyù dàolù'' *we must persist in stimulating [[social harmony]]; 必须坚持促进社会和谐; ''Bìxū jiānchí cùjìn shèhuì héxié'' *we must persist in [[peaceful development]]; 必须坚持和平发展; ''Bìxū jiānchí hépíng fāzhǎn'' *we must persist in the leadership of the Party. 必须坚持党的领导; ''Bìxū jiānchí dǎng de lǐngdǎo''<ref>[https://chinacopyrightandmedia.wordpress.com/2013/01/17/eight-musts-coalesce-into-consensus/ “Eight Musts” Coalesce into Consensus] Posted on January 17, 2013</ref>
